<i>it was too hot, I had a headache.</i>

556
00:47:48,645 --> 00:47:51,484
<i>Nino was probably</i>
<i>still in love with Lila.</i>

557
00:47:52,564 --> 00:47:55,444
<i>In the course of his life</i>
<i>he would love only her,</i>

558
00:47:55,524 --> 00:47:57,884
