687
01:00:35,085 --> 01:00:36,325
Stop!

688
01:00:40,645 --> 01:00:42,245
Don't speak!

689
01:00:44,605 --> 01:00:47,044
Now you go and tell your daughters.

690
01:00:47,125 --> 01:00:48,725
